{"tid":1286194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民建聯社區主任在房署租辦事處可能唔洗錢","createTime":"2019-07-04T20:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T23:09:21.000Z","uid":265546,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8c3b968ad254dfc9477a683f92bc294c0f6a4be4","tid":1286194,"uid":265546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T20:31:26.000Z","msg":"注冊團體&ldquo;公屋聯會&rdquo;（以優惠租金租用）的各區地辦事處都會提供比民建聯做區內社區主任的地辦（所有區都有），點解唔佢哋自己租地方用呢？係咪有利益輸送呢？房署點解唔管呢？選舉經費又計唔計呢？<br />\n之前問過房署，佢地話管唔到，我將會出信比房署署長要求交代，兄弟各自做野啦！（各聯會門口會貼滿建制poster，記得有圖有證據呀~）<br />\n（Share比房署商業租戶可能會嬲嬲豬囉咁平租）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rEjcNJH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrEjcNJH.jpg&h=c4f9f20a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公屋聯會<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkph.org/main/contact/sub.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkph.org%2Fmain%2Fcontact%2Fsub.html&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVc4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=462766c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkph.org/main/contact/sub.html</a><br />\n九龍社團聯會<br />\n<a href=\"https://klnfas.hk/tc/%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%83%E7%B0%A1%E4%BB%8BMgvsac627ab1ccbdb62ec96e702f07f6425bZ062fddee8df90b1a0c77860a52b4d68ddoFcw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fklnfas.hk%2Ftc%2F%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25B0%25A1%25E4%25BB%258BMgvsac627ab1ccbdb62ec96e702f07f6425bZ062fddee8df90b1a0c77860a52b4d68ddoFcw&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVc4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=16f5c69c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://klnfas.hk/tc/%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%83%E7%B0%A1%E4%BB%8BMgvsac627ab1ccbdb62ec96e702f07f6425bZ062fddee8df90b1a0c77860a52b4d68ddoFcw</a><br />\n民建聯 各社區主任 <br />\n（fb大把地址自己搵）<br />\n<br />\n房屋署社福服務用途單位<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/commercial-properties/leasing-information/welfare-lettings/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.housingauthority.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcommercial-properties%2Fleasing-information%2F